Thanks<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><p>nir<br><a href=mailto:"emoticon.master@spiritoftunare.com">emoticon.master@spiritoftunare.com</a><BR><font color=red>*<8-)</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udalzuth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dalzuth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/29/01 8:17:34 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> I'm in the same boat here...  I've heard it's 36 hours after server up/last death too, but I've also been told that you have to kill CT first.  Anyone know for sure?<br>
<br>
Thanks,<br>
<br>
Dalzuth <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uankhamun.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ankhamun</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/29/01 2:15:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> Blah there is NO good info out there on his spawn time.  This is what just happened on me on Brell. <br>
Broken Golem went down Friday night 11:48 PST.... didn't spawn Saturday night, didn't spawn Sunday night.  I went into fear Monday at 5:30pm PST and he was up.  I also got his oil not even an hour before our server crashed and depopped fear &lt;thank god&gt;  So anyway, I'm going for the 48-72 hour theory.  <br>
<br>
Ankhamun <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/utargonis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Targonis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/30/01 6:08:02 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> One theory is that it's a 24 hour spawn that skips spawns, up to 72 hours.  Another is that it's purely random after 24 hours.<br>
<br>
Your best bet is to make friends in lots of guilds, and when you see them show up, ask them if they have any information on if it's up or not.  You can often do a /who all 47 50 wiz, and check what low level wizards are up there who CAN'T trigger themselves, and who might let you know if the current raid is planning on using the broken or not.  Not just for the epic, but in general, I've found it a LOT easier to make pick-up groups this way as well.<br>
 <p>Targonis Manastorm<br>
Level 59 Wizard<br>
Bloodguard of Souls<br>
The Nameless Server<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udalzuth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dalzuth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/30/01 1:04:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> So, the golem has nothing to do with whether CT is killed or not? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/urombusmindspire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rombus Mindspire</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><table width=111><tr><td style=filter:glow(color=#6633FF strength=1);font-family:arial;font-weight;bold;font-size:'1pt' nowrap><font size=1 color=#FFFFFF face=Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif>Forum Sorcerer</font></td></tr></table></span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/30/01 1:22:59 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://wots-signatures.hypermart.net/rombus/sidepic.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> After what I've seen for the past couple of weeks, I'm going for 24+ hours purly and totally random.  As stated, there's no good spawn time info on this mob.<br>
<br>
