<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umuldamai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Muldamai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/4/01 7:20:41 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> The best I can say, its like stalking the AC in South Ro, just harder. I have been on 3 raids to kill CT after he has been ubered, and when we have the plain mostly clear and we are headed to CT, the broken golem has spawned. If it was a repop from something, or a triggered reaction, couldnt tell ya.<br>
<br>
If it happened 2 times, I would go with luck. It happened 3 times, so who knows. Just take your 2 week vacation if you want him that bad, and spend every day in Fear. (j/k, Go away and dont think about the epic for 2 weeks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Muldamai<br>
