<br>
Endaar<br>
 <p><IMG SRC="http://www.prudenteauto.com/Sigs/EndaarSig0824.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/unlaren.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nlaren</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/8/01 8:26:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> After the Enraged Golem was killed that Monday evening/Tuesday morning on Karana, the Broken golem respawned at around 4am EST Friday morning.  This was at 72 hours since it was last killed.  Cazic was up when the broken golem spawned.  We had just killed Dread, Fright, and Terror (I believe in that order). <p>Nlaren Manaweaver
<br>Wizard of the 54th</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uicetoadeq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>icetoadeq</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/12/01 4:18:49 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> I have been timing the spawn for the last 3 weeks or so and I am almost totally sure that its 48 after patch, and 24 ever time he dies.  <p><P align="center"><A HREF="mailto:icetoad15@aol.com"><IMG SRC=http://www.hneguild.com/sigs/sig_icetoad.jpg border="0"></A></P>
<P align="center">- 57<sup>th</sup> Evoker of Heaven and Earth, Saryrn Server</P> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=british>British</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(9/13/01 9:37:33 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Golem spawn time</span><hr size=1> I just killed him last night around 11:00 PM ish PST.<br>
<br>
He had been up for several hours at least, and the regularly scheduled Fear raid that evening ran out of steam and quit, leaving the path clear for me and my guild to swoop in and snatch it up later.  <br>
<br>
So, I'm not sure exactly what time he spawned but it was well before 36 hours, giving more credibility to the 24 hour after server restart theory.<br>
<br>
All I have left is Mr. Fishhead now!<br>
<br>
